{"tid":2168742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：或強制分開不同員工執枱與傳菜　進食後聊天都要戴口罩","createTime":"2020-08-22T03:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T12:08:18.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9b82256c584c60c8d100a3fad6428e5903d03b","tid":2168742,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，如要放寬社交距離措施，要有足夠信心疫情緩和，確診數字持續下降及隱形傳播鏈減少等。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始出席本台節目《星期六問責》表示，確診數字持續下降是要看到相關趨勢，並非一兩天的數字。她又說，過去個多月，明白巿民好忍耐，也明白巿民與業界對食肆堂食的需求很大，但要安心放寬措施，食肆合作亦很重要。<span class=\"red\">她提到有專家指出，如果執枱與傳菜同屬一人，會有傳播風險，至於是否強制分開不同員工進行，要與業界溝通。陳肇始又說，在食肆內除下口罩聊天的傳播風險大，要考慮是否當進食後聊天都要戴口罩等安排</span>，又說食肆空氣流通亦減低風險，如果食肆願意合作，在資源方面都可以商討。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，要留意最近有群組爆發，令人擔心，包括外傭宿舍及貨櫃碼頭群組，兩者正進行檢測工作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545248-20200822.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545248-20200822.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=3624b8ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545248-20200822.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e37b6e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545248-20200822.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"18cfc553499629f506f77289624dc141b54dcfab","tid":2168742,"uid":365024,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"Hi 君君"},{"pid":"320296e90458107f7fefe3fbcd7d86253d567ffa","tid":2168742,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">屌</span>"},{"pid":"b2f567a4a9c2f610a2bdc6a3e88f4a09c480b946","tid":2168742,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18cfc553499629f506f77289624dc141b54dcfab","tid":2168742,"uid":365024,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:37:07.000Z